Then it replaces links (e.g. [Link text](http://www.example.com)) with HTML links (e.g. <a href="http://www.example.com">Link text</a>).

Finally, it replaces markdown headers (e.g. ### Heading 3) with HTML headers (e.g. <h3>Heading 3</h3>).

